Privacy Policy
Privacy policy for Bible4kidz
1. Content
The Bible4kidz app respects your privacy. This privacy statement describes how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use the Bible4kidz app and this website.
2.Data collection
Our app does not collect any personal data from users. All data is collected by Google to deliver the service.
The information we gather comes from following sources:
Information you provide us: We collect information you provide us directly, such as when you make a gift or when you contact us. This may include information such as name, email address, phone number, date of birth, and postal address.
Information we collect automatically: We collect information automatically when you use the website, such as information about your device, your browser, and your usage patterns. This may include information such as IP address, operating system, browser type, reference page, visited pages, and time of visit.
Information from third parties: We may receive information about you from third parties, such as from social media platforms or from other apps you use. This may include information such as name, email address, and profile information.
3. Permissions
Our app does not use any permissions.
4. Use of information
We use the information we collect for several purposes, including:
To deliver and improve Bible4kidz and this website
To communicate with you about Bible4kidz and this website
To market our products and services
To comply with the Accounting Act’s requirements for the storage of accounting figures
To prevent fraud and abuse
5. Sharing of information
We may share the information we collect with third parties, including:
Suppliers who help us deliver and improve Bible4kidz and this website
Tax authorities upon request
The accounting office for accounting purposes
Other companies that we collaborate with
We will never sell or rent out your personal information to third parties without your consent.
6. Your choices
You have several choices when it comes to the information we collect about you. You can:
Update or delete your information by logging into my page or contacting us
here
.
Unsubscribe from newsletters by clicking on the “unsubscribe” link in the emails we send you.
Block third-party cookies in your browser.
7. Security
We use security measures to protect your information from loss, misuse, and unauthorized access, use, alteration, or disclosure.
8. Children
Bible4kidz is aimed at children under 13 years of age. We do not collect any information about you through the use of the Bible4kidz app, other than what Google collects to provide you with this service.
9. Changes
We may update this privacy statement from time to time. The latest version will always be available on this page.
10. Contact us
If you have questions or concerns about your privacy, you can contact us
here
.
11. Legislation
This privacy statement is subject to Norwegian law.